snippet.textDisplay:
बिरोबा च्या नावानं गा ....चांगभलं 
Everything is good as we chant name of lord Biroba

ज्योतिबाच्या नावानं ...... चांगभलं 
Everything is good as we chant name of lord Jyotiba

सुंबरान मांडलं गा सुंबरान मांडलं 
तवाच्या येळला येळच्या गा घडीला
now for every moment we are here to remember (doing  स्मरण )our lords (Lord Jyotiba and Lord Biroba ) 

पयलं माझं नमन गणपती देवाला 
my first obeisance is to lord ganesha

दुसरं माझं नमन बसलेल्या सभंला 
my second obeisance is to all devotees sitting and listening to us

अन तिसरं माझं नमन कैलासाच्या सांबाला 
and my obeisance is to lord shiva from mount kailash
